The '''University of Ketaris''' was an institution of higher learning that offered courses in [[Xenoarchaeology/Legends|xenoarchaeology]]. One of the students there was [[Naj Pandoor]]. At some point prior to the outbreak of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the University went bankrupt.

